# career-kit tracks ONLY kit-authored files.
#
# Everything setup.sh materializes into this directory — the career-ops
# upstream (scaffolded by `npx @santifer/career-ops init`), node_modules,
# and every piece of personal data (config/profile.yml, cv.md, data/*,
# reports/*, output/*, data/answers.yml with salary and EEO answers) —
# stays untracked by design. The whitelist below is the complete list of
# tracked paths; add new kit files here explicitly.
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/SETUP.md
!/setup.sh
!/overlay/
!/seed/
!/docs/
/docs/*
!/docs/TEST-CHECKLIST.md
!/docs/POE-VARIANT.md
!/docs/FALLBACKS.md
!/docs/UPDATING.md
